# SSH hosts for distributed training — one hostname or IP per line.
# Lines starting with '#' are ignored.
#
# The FIRST non-comment line becomes the rendezvous master (rdzv_endpoint).
# All nodes must have passwordless SSH access from the machine running launch_distributed.py.
# All nodes must have the repo cloned to the same --workdir path.
#
# Example:
# node0.mycluster.local
# node1.mycluster.local
# 192.168.1.10
# 192.168.1.11
